        "id": 1114919
      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-10-21T20:34:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I store tuples in stack to decode whether children were visited already or this initial \"touch\" of the node:\n\nstack.push((root, false))\nwhile stack:\n  node, children_emitted \u003d stack.pop()\n  if children_emitted:\n    emit(node)\n  else:\n    stack.push((node, true))\n    for child in node.children:\n      stack.push((child, false))\n  \nstill, for O(1M) nodes we have + Golang, it doesn\u0027t matter really.",
